            "parameters": {
                "text": "=You are a cybersecurity threat intelligence analyst.\n\nAnalyze this IP address data and generate a threat assessment report.\n\nIP ADDRESS: \n{{ $('Set IP Address1').item.json.ip_address }}\nGEOLOCATION DATA:\n{{ $json.city }}\n{{ $json.region }}\n{{ $json.region_code }}\n{{ $json.country_name }}\n\nVIRUSTOTAL DATA:\n{{ $('VirusTotal HTTP Request1').item.json.data }}\n\nYour task:\n1. Analyze the IP for malicious indicators\n2. Evaluate geolocation, ASN, and reputation data\n3. Review VirusTotal detection results\n4. Assign risk level: LOW / MEDIUM / HIGH / CRITICAL\n\nReturn ONLY valid Plaintext in this structure:\n\n  \"ip_address\": \"x.x.x.x\",\n  \"risk_level\": \"LOW|MEDIUM|HIGH|CRITICAL\",\n  \"summary\": \"Brief 2-3 sentence overview\",\n  \"geolocation\": \n    \"country\": \"\",\n    \"region\": \"\",\n    \"city\": \"\",\n    \"asn\": \"\",\n    \"org\": \"\"\n  \n  \"virustotal\": \n    \"detections\": \"X/XX\",\n    \"reputation\": 0,\n    \"last_analysis\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\"\n  \n  \"key_findings\": [\"finding1\", \"finding2\", \"finding3\"],\n  \"recommendation\": \"Actionable recommendation\"\n",
